  We outdamage EVERY OTHER CLASS BAR NONE. I have yet to see ANYONE take down a mob faster than a mage. Between our pets and our offense-only spells, the target is never long for this world =) Yes necros are much more mana efficient than mages when it comes to killing, but necros rely heavily upon fear kiting, whereas I tend to kill my targets where they stand. Even now, when i solo, the avg life expectancy of my target is AT MOST 17 seconds. Usually I do them in 9-12 seconds. <br>
  I cant port, and that blows. I cant evac, another downside. But I can solo and farm and OBLITERATE with my spells and pet. I dont know what youre lookin for from the game, and I know that for some ppl its not the stats or popularity, but the title. What they wanna BE in game. Ive got a few friends that only play certain classes because thats what they played when they played D&amp;D. Call it nostalgia I guess...whatever makes ya happy =)<br>
